  "detailed_description": "<h1>Feature List</h1><p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Levels: Explore 20+ new levels filled with hidden objects. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Minigames: Enjoy a variety of 70+ calming minigames. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gardens: Expand and personalize your garden sanctuary. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Music: Relax with gentle, soothing music. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scenes: Discover beautifully handcrafted nature settings.</p></li></ul></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the gentle embrace of nature once again with Nature Escapes 4. This latest chapter in the series invites you to explore 24 peaceful levels, each one thoughtfully crafted to transport you into the heart of the natural world. The beauty of nature is just a screen away, offering a quiet moment of reflection and discovery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517920/extras/f4f38e4339f084e13c77e212093072e5.poster.avif?t=1729642403\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517920/extras/f4f38e4339f084e13c77e212093072e5.webm?t=1729642403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517920/extras/f4f38e4339f084e13c77e212093072e5.mp4?t=1729642403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Nature Escapes 4, the experience is both familiar and fresh. The game’s calming atmosphere remains, but now there’s even more to explore and enjoy. Find hidden treasures nestled within lush landscapes, and take your time expanding your garden with new plants and decorations that reflect the beauty you uncover. It’s a journey through serene scenes, where every level is a new escape into tranquility.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517920/extras/3c86ebe65bfd54232cfb5405ffcbe167.poster.avif?t=1729642403\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517920/extras/3c86ebe65bfd54232cfb5405ffcbe167.webm?t=1729642403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517920/extras/3c86ebe65bfd54232cfb5405ffcbe167.mp4?t=1729642403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Let Nature Escapes 4 be your retreat into the calm, where the simple joy of finding hidden objects and creating your own sanctuary awaits.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the gentle embrace of nature once again with Nature Escapes 4. This latest chapter in the series invites you to explore 24 peaceful levels, each one thoughtfully crafted to transport you into the heart of the natural world. The beauty of nature is just a screen away, offering a quiet moment of reflection and discovery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517920/extras/f4f38e4339f084e13c77e212093072e5.poster.avif?t=1729642403\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517920/extras/f4f38e4339f084e13c77e212093072e5.webm?t=1729642403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517920/extras/f4f38e4339f084e13c77e212093072e5.mp4?t=1729642403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Nature Escapes 4, the experience is both familiar and fresh. The game’s calming atmosphere remains, but now there’s even more to explore and enjoy. Find hidden treasures nestled within lush landscapes, and take your time expanding your garden with new plants and decorations that reflect the beauty you uncover. It’s a journey through serene scenes, where every level is a new escape into tranquility.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517920/extras/3c86ebe65bfd54232cfb5405ffcbe167.poster.avif?t=1729642403\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517920/extras/3c86ebe65bfd54232cfb5405ffcbe167.webm?t=1729642403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517920/extras/3c86ebe65bfd54232cfb5405ffcbe167.mp4?t=1729642403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Let Nature Escapes 4 be your retreat into the calm, where the simple joy of finding hidden objects and creating your own sanctuary awaits.</p>",
